{
  "texts": [
    "In some schools with sufficient teaching equipment and teacher resources, it is possible to carry out quality education.",
    "However, in some areas with high competitive pressure, many school leaders may not conscientiously implement this reform proposal.",
    "Instead of caring about the future development of students, they are more concerned about how many students can be to good universities.",
    "The solution I can think of is that schools in the same area can conduct cross-school teaching research and exchanges to share their quality education courses and results.",
    "The Education Bureau should make these activities part of the school assessment."
  ]
}